d Context: May 2025 - Version 0.50 (Major Update)**\nWhile not in February, the **v0.50 release in May 2025** was a significant milestone that introduced:\n- **Max Mode** - Official launch with support for all top-tier AI models, transparent token-based pricing\n- **Background Agent** - Early preview of parallel running agents with independent remote environments\n- **New Tab Model** - Enhanced cross-file suggestions and editing capabilities\n- **Chat improvements** - Export to Markdown, copy existing chats for parallel exploration\n- **Multi-root workspace support** - Better management of multiple projects\n- **Inline editing updates** - New look with full file editing and agent handoff capabilities\n\n## Summary\nWhile the specific official changelog for February 2025 isn't detailed in the search results, the timeline shows that **February 2025 (v0.46)** marked an important milestone with Agent becoming the default mode, UI refreshes, and web search integration - setting the stage for the more substantial v0.50 release that came later in May.\n\nFor the most detailed and official changelog information, I'd recommend checking Cursor's official website or release notes directly, as these search results primarily show aggregated information from Chinese tech blogs and documentation sites.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
